description.plain:
Christopher Daniel Soriano (b. January 4, 1997), better known by his stage name CJ, is a rapper coming out of Staten Island, New York. He also has a Puerto Rican background.

CJ began his musical career in 2017 at the age of 20 years old. He first gained some traction with the release of his 2018 song “Pop” featuring 6ix9ine. He didn’t take off however until late 2020 when his hit song “Whoopty” blew up on TikTok.

On February 19, 2021, CJ released his debut EP, Loyalty Over Royalty.

songs.title: Whoopty

description.plain:
“Whoopty” is a single by rapper CJ. Released in July 2020, the music video has surpassed millions of views on YouTube.

It uses the same sample from the Bollywood song “Sanam Re” that was also used in the  “Exposing Me” beat popularized by Memo 600 and used by King Von, FBG Duck, Pop Smoke, Rah Swish, and others.

description.plain:
Es la pista que lo puso en el mapa. CJ está de regreso una vez más con el segundo remix oficial de su exitoso sencillo, “Whoopty”. Sirve como el principal y único sencillo antes del lanzamiento de la edición de lujo de Loyalty Over Royalty. Fue lanzado el 26 de Marzo de 2021.

En esta segunda remezcla oficial, CJ recluta a dos de los artistas en ascenso de Puerto Rico, Anuell AA y Ozuna, para que rapeen sobre sus salvajes estilos de vida de romper opps y ganar dinero.

Gracias al éxito tanto de la canción original como de este segundo remix, la canción ganó una atención masiva entre los oyentes españoles, lo que finalmente resultó en que CJ recibiera una atención masiva en la música latina.

songs.title: “BOP”

description.plain:
“BOP” is the second single from rapper CJ, released on January 25th, 2021. This serves as his first release of the year, as well as being the follow-up single to his breakout song, Whoopty. It also marks as the third track to CJ’s debut EP, Loyalty Over Royalty.

The song was first teased on his Instagram page, where he showed off a snippet of the song, as well as previewing the visuals, alongside of it.

On January 25th, the music video and song was uploaded to YouTube, and announced that the song would be uploaded to streaming platforms on January 26th.
